{"tid":733730,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人好怕坐長途機","createTime":"2018-07-08T04:31:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-08T05:32:40.000Z","uid":133304,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e9c13096c638468ebfd3fbe1ff303931f37e1f98","tid":733730,"uid":133304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T04:31:06.000Z","msg":"坐喺度十幾個鐘，瞓又難瞓又伸展唔到，位本身窄又有壓逼感<br />\n有時辛苦起嚟真係飛機餐都食唔落<br />\n（個人本身已經覺得飛機啲空氣有啲令人唔舒服嘅味，聞到好易作悶頭暈）<br />\nDelay嘅話仲辛苦，航程已經耐仲要坐完又坐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係好佩服啲人落機個樣仲咁容光煥發，我落機成條行屍咁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55d8b1835e5e3fc199fddd631a106232d9e061ec","tid":733730,"uid":4431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T05:02:53.000Z","msg":"應該無人會鍾意呀嘛，除非有班靚飛雞輪住同我坐就唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab0a17d4c25e3b0d71d70e0eb50715f67ab3e21a","tid":733730,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T05:16:00.000Z","msg":"短長都驚"},{"pid":"015d986c0c5b0fc3056a9d27ca304f045a561dc1","tid":733730,"uid":13718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T05:32:40.000Z","msg":"我覺得&gt;9個鐘已經冇感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}